  "instructions": [
    "Melt 2 tablespoons of butter in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onions and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the gluten-free flour and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Slowly pour in the white wine, whisking continuously to avoid lumps.",
    "Add the fish stock and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the cod fish and cook until it flakes easily with a fork, about 5 minutes.",
    " Stir in the coconut milk and heavy cream. Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Season the bisque with salt, black pepper, and lemon juice.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the bisque hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley if desired."
  ],
